window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>I trusted my heart to a vampire. Now I want revenge....</b><br> <br> The vampires are at war, and I’m caught in the middle. I thought nothing could surpass my desire for Nic’s dark, dangerous charms, but with my father dead from the fangs of our enemy, everything has changed.</p> <p>I’m consumed with the need to seek vengeance. Suddenly, I realize what I must do. I ask Nic to change me. He forbids it. He tells me the change must be made for the right reason. For love. And avenging my father isn’t the right reason.</p> <p>But with our enemy closing in fast, I’m angry enough to defy Nic and fight this war my way, no matter what the consequences.</p>"; 
